nvcontrol (0.8.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Legacy GPU detection with deprecation warnings for Maxwell/Pascal on 590+
  * Explicit Sync commands (nvctl wayland explicit-sync status/enable)
  * Top-level HDR command (status, enable, disable, config, set-brightness)
  * DLSS 4.5 support with Multi-Frame Generation for RTX 50 series
  * Kubernetes GPU detection with cluster capacity reporting
  * Documentation updates with explicit sync guide

 -- CK Technology LLC <info@cktechx.com>  Mon, 13 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000

